    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Knives in a place setting that are designed and used for consuming the main meal, typically excluding dessert. For similar knives in a more formal setting, in which there may be a number of other knives of various design and for various purposes, use "entrée knives" for the knife intended for the main course.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
